RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 1M 70Y All Weather Track CR: 57. Maiden Claiming Purse 21000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 118 lbs. Claiming Price $16,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: RED SUN DRESS laid off the pace in the three path, ranged up in the four path around the far turn, swept to the lead turning into the stretch, and was driven clear. TOURIST STYLE broke out bumping an outer foe, rated inside, tipped out to the six path going into the far turn, fanned out to the eight path into the stretch, and kept on for place. SPANISH GIRL got bumped at the start by an inner foe, tracked in the three path, was coaxed into the far turn, angled out to the six path turning into the lane, and finished evenly on her left lead for show. WONDERFULVENEZUELA chased in the two path, tipped to the rail under a drive turning into the stretch, but flattened. DREAMY broke out and bumped an outer foe, stalked in the five path, bid in the four path around the far turn, but faded from the five path in the stretch. MAELSTROM SPIRIT got pinched at the start, trailed in the three path, and did not factor in from the six path in the stretch. FUMBLEROOSKI raced up close along the inside, vied for the lead midway down the backstretch, but gaveway from the rail around the far turn. CAJUN ANTHEM had an awkward start, led from the three path into the backstretch, vied with an inner foe midway down the backstretch, was roused while shifting inside early into the far turn, but faded from the three path down the lane.
